properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the DisplaySetting.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the DisplaySetting with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.name: itemByRange
methods.description: Returns the DisplaySettings within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The DisplaySetting, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: DisplaySetting, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The DisplaySetting, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: DisplaySetting, Long Integer or String.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first DisplaySetting in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last DisplaySetting in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle DisplaySetting in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem
methods.description: Returns the DisplaySetting with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the DisplaySetting that follows the desired DisplaySetting.

methods.name: nextItem
methods.description: Returns the DisplaySetting whose index follows the specified DisplaySetting in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The DisplaySetting whose index comes before the desired DisplaySetting.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any DisplaySetting in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
methods.description: Returns every DisplaySetting in the collection.
